&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culture: &lt;/strong&gt;A supportive, inclusive culture that encourages innovation, safety, and creative risk-taking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Community:&lt;/strong&gt; Paid volunteer opportunities and regular DEI celebrations to foster a strong sense of community and collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
