&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Deliver measurable growth in revenue and customer acquisition through expert management of Google Shopping, Performance Max, and Search.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Optimize efficiency through structured testing, smart bidding, and strategic budget allocation to ensure we are leading, not following, in the SEM space.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with Product teams to unlock incremental performance by improving our product feed strategy and data quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
